{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/Lockman\/documentation\/Lockman"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/lockman\/debuggingguide"]}],"metadata":{"role":"article","roleHeading":"Article","title":"Debugging Guide","modules":[{"name":"Lockman"}]},"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/Lockman\/documentation\/Lockman\/DebuggingGuide","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"kind":"article","abstract":[{"text":"Learn how to debug Lockman-related issues in your application.","type":"text"}],"seeAlsoSections":[{"anchor":"Essentials","title":"Essentials","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/Lockman\/documentation\/Lockman\/GettingStarted","doc:\/\/Lockman\/documentation\/Lockman\/BoundaryOverview","doc:\/\/Lockman\/documentation\/Lockman\/Lock","doc:\/\/Lockman\/documentation\/Lockman\/Unlock","doc:\/\/Lockman\/documentation\/Lockman\/ChoosingStrategy","doc:\/\/Lockman\/documentation\/Lockman\/Configuration","doc:\/\/Lockman\/documentation\/Lockman\/ErrorHandling"]}],"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","type":"heading","anchor":"Overview","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Debugging issues in applications using Lockman requires a different approach from traditional debugging due to the complexity of exclusive control. LockmanManager provides powerful debugging features for developers to monitor lock states and identify problems.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"By utilizing appropriate debugging tools, you can efficiently identify and resolve lock conflicts, deadlocks, performance issues, and more.","type":"text"}]},{"text":"LockmanManager Debug Features","type":"heading","anchor":"LockmanManager-Debug-Features","level":2},{"text":"Enabling Debug Logs","type":"heading","anchor":"Enabling-Debug-Logs","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Lockman provides detailed lock operation logs:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ Enable debug logs (only works in DEBUG builds)","LockmanManager.debug.isLoggingEnabled = true"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Log output example","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["✅ [Lockman] canLock succeeded - Strategy: SingleExecution, BoundaryId: process, Info: LockmanSingleExecutionInfo(actionId: 'startProcessButtonTapped', uniqueId: 7BFC785A-3D25-4722-B9BC-A3A63A7F49FC, mode: boundary)","","❌ [Lockman] canLock failed - Strategy: SingleExecution, BoundaryId: process, Info: LockmanSingleExecutionInfo(actionId: 'startProcessButtonTapped', uniqueId: 1EBA9632-DE39-43B6-BE75-7C754476CD4E, mode: boundary), Reason: Boundary 'process' already has an active lock","","⚠️ [Lockman] canLock succeeded with cancellation - Strategy: PriorityBased, BoundaryId: sync, Info: LockmanPriorityBasedInfo(...), Cancelled: 'backgroundSync' (uniqueId: 123e4567-e89b-12d3-a456-426614174000), Error: LockmanPriorityBasedCancellationError"],"syntax":null},{"text":"Current Lock State Display","type":"heading","anchor":"Current-Lock-State-Display","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You can display lock states in table format:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ Display current lock state","LockmanManager.debug.printCurrentLocks()"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Output example"}]},{"type":"text","text":":"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["┌─────────────────┬──────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────┬─────────────────┐","│ Strategy        │ BoundaryId       │ ActionId\/UniqueId                    │ Additional Info │","├─────────────────┼──────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────┼─────────────────┤","│ SingleExecution │ CancelID.process │ startProcessButtonTapped             │ mode: boundary  │","│                 │                  │ 08CC1862-136F-4643-A796-F63156D8BF56 │                 │","├─────────────────┼──────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────┼─────────────────┤","│ PriorityBased   │ CancelID.sync    │ backgroundSync                       │ priority: .low  │","│                 │                  │ 987f6543-a21b-34c5-d678-123456789012 │ behavior: .rep..│","└─────────────────┴──────────────────┴──────────────────────────────────────┴─────────────────┘"],"syntax":null},{"anchor":"Format-Options","type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Format Options"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You can customize the display format:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ Compact display (for narrow terminals)","LockmanManager.debug.printCurrentLocks(options: .compact)","","\/\/ Detailed display","LockmanManager.debug.printCurrentLocks(options: .detailed)","","\/\/ Custom format","let customOptions = LockmanManager.debug.FormatOptions(","    useShortStrategyNames: true,","    simplifyBoundaryIds: true,","    maxStrategyWidth: 15,","    maxBoundaryWidth: 20",")","LockmanManager.debug.printCurrentLocks(options: customOptions)"],"syntax":"swift"},{"anchor":"Cleanup-Feature","type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Cleanup Feature"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"You can reset problematic lock states:"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["\/\/ Clean up all locks from all strategies","LockmanManager.cleanup.all()","","\/\/ Clean up locks only for specific boundary","LockmanManager.cleanup.boundary(CancelID.userAction)"],"syntax":"swift"}]}],"references":{"doc://Lockman/documentation/Lockman":{"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"Elegant exclusive control for user actions in The Composable Architecture applications.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/Lockman\/documentation\/Lockman","url":"\/documentation\/lockman","title":"Lockman","role":"collection"},"doc://Lockman/documen